Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:14.18,sign_53_2_More_corpses_wer,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2009,1)}More corpses were produced\N in those 88 days than ever \Nbefore in the history of \Nthe Yokohama underground
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:14.18,sign_53_3_Numerous_organiz,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2009,1)}Numerous organizations \Nwere involved in the\N whirlwind of bloodshed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:04.08,Stray Dogs - Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,More corpses were produced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:07.32,Stray Dogs - Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,in those 88 days than ever before in the \Nhistory of the Yokohama underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:11.07,Stray Dogs - Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Numerous organizations were involved \Nin the whirlwind of bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.21,Stray Dogs - Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Head Conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.18,sign_281_7_The_Dragon__Head,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}The Dragon\N Head Conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:22.23,sign_383_9__One_year_earlie,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1255,3841)\fs20\c&H240486&\b1}One year earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:19.46,Stray Dogs - Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One year earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:40.76,Stray Dogs - Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,there's no escaping gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill everyone \Nin the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.08,sign_1579_14_Episode__26,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode\N 26
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.08,sign_1579_15_Dazai___Chuuya__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai, \NChuuya, \NFifteen \NYears \NOld
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:21.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:25.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Our weapons smugglers are \Ntwo weeks behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:31.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Our men are going to be fighting \Nwith kitchen knives at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,and that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:37.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,With the escalating violence, we're losing \Ncontracts for our protection business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we just aren't cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:45.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Dazai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:52.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Not having money, not having intel, \Nnot having the trust of your subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that from the \Nbeginning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:00.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why are you mixing \Nhypertension medication
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,with hypotension medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:07.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I thought taking them together \Nmight be a comfortable way to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:14.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,you were there when \NI inherited the boss's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:17.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You're a witness for his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you dying so willy-nilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.53,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:31.70,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor... tell the executives \Nto murder them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:35.14,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,The opposing organizations, \Nthe military police,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.87,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,everyone who opposes the \NPort Mafia, by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.25,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a rational course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.41,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how many men we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.42,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.33,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.82,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:46.72,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:47.83,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.11,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.85,Stray Dogs - Flashback - top,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.93,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,The boss has passed on due to his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.61,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,He left word saying I will \Ninherit his position as the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.36,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You're my witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.29,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You made an error in judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:18.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It was smart of you to choose someone\N who attempts suicide as your accomplice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:21.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but here I am a year later, alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I made no error.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You and I were successful \Nin our mission together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:33.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The mission isn't complete \Nuntil those who were involved
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,in the assassination are silenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,To that end, I was a perfect accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I ended my life in a suicide \Nof unknown motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,after you became the \Nboss thanks to my testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,no one would suspect a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You remind me of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:58.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,If I was going to silence you, \NI would have done it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:03.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want, I can prepare something \Nthat'll end your life comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:07.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I want to ask you \Nto do a quick investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,There's no danger involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds so sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:17.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I trust that you know about Suribachi City \Nin the Yokohama settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:23.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor going around that a certain \Nindividual has emerged in that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:26.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to investigate that rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:31.16,Stray Dogs - Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:31.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,This contract is a delegation of authority. \NThey call it the "Silver Message."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:36.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Show this to any Port Mafia member\Nand they'll do anything you ask of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the rumor about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A rumor that's harmful just by spreading...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's the previous boss, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:59.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,There are some humans who must \Nnever rise from the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll promise to make me that drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be your first job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this person I remind you of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-kun, why do you wish to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:34.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think there's any \Nvalue in the act of living?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,The Yokohama foreign settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a giant explosion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:50.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,In the resulting crater,\N people began building a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirozu,0000,0000,0000,,That's this place: Suribachi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.79,sign_8539_98_The_Complete__Gu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Complete\N Guide to\N Suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So they drink metal plating to \Nkill themselves overseas, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:04.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But those who have their \Norgans melted while they're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Glad I didn't try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hirotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:21.24,Stray Dogs - Italics,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,This boy was there with the boss \Nwhen the previous boss passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.85,Stray Dogs - Italics,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't underestimate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,This area is in a state of conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Conflict?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:37.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,The Port Mafia currently has \Nthree enemy organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,One is Takasekai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Another is GSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,And, lastly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:47.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,a complementary army comprised \Nentirely of juveniles, the Sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:51.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I found the previous boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,From the pits of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a proper \Nreport when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,A kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:28.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,The Port Mafia must be really \Ndesperate for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I hate pain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Die now, or die after you \Ngive me information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Either's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,All the better if you can \Nkill me comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you just a suicidal brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're a brat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just any brat, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:59.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me about this \N"Arahabaki" that you're snooping on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Arahabaki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:06.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,You know about it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:18.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Those who step into the Sheep's territory \Nwill be met with fierce retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the King of the Sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Nakahara Chuuya, manipulator of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen to have a card up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're a cocky, over-confident child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're the kind of person I hate the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:42.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate condescending little pricks like \Nyou more than anything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,You're not scaring me, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Sheep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,No, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen to have a good card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,The card of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gifted, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:11.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hirotsu-san, this kid controls the \Ngravity of anything he touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Port Mafia for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting more from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability isn't going to work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost your grip on gravity now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,With my ability of nullifying \Nthe powers of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for you to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He kicked me before you used your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:19.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He used his ability to fly backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He took no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like dealing \Nwith you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hirotsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The previous boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.97,Stray Dogs - Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Port Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:06.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Nakahara Chuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored to have been invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:15.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you put on quite the \Nshow with my men yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Not for long, before someone got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:22.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm sure you brought \Nme here in regards to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,What are you investigating \Nin regards to Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,You! You're that suicidal \Nkid from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I'm glad you're \Nas full of energy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:43.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm injured pretty badly \Nover here, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:47.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You two seem to have hit it off, \Nhaving known each other for just a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:53.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'd like to chat with you \Nabout what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please release him, Randou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:59.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I can't recommend that, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,This boy is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I have measures in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:08.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Randou-kun, you look colder than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:09.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed to admit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm freezing and could die any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Cold? Dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You may step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:22.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,How could he be cold at \Nthis time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably just chickening out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:31.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:36.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,he's a secondary executive and \Nan excellent ability user.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-san, why don't you \Nget to business already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:48.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun, are you interested in \Naffiliating with the Port Mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:57.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's the reaction \NI should have expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Still, our goals are aligned somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You could decide after we evaluate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:08.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,what we can offer each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:13.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare tell me you've forgotten \Nwhat you've done to this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Our previous boss's rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:20.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The tyranny of that man, who led the city \Ninto a state of violence and terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,is still fresh in everyone's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:27.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,But that man is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:36.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,If there is such a rumor, \Nthat such bloody rule has returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,we must find the truth about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you be worried, otherwise, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard some damning \Nrumors about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:50.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,That the old boss might not have\N died of illness, but was murdered by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Who could believe that he said,\N in his final moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,that he'd give his position \Nto a mere doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I killed the previous boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I slashed the great boss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:09.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,with this scalpel and made it \Nlook like a death by disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:21.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun, I'd like to ask you to \Nparticipate in a joint investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:25.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The rumors we've heard about \Nthe previous boss's return
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,and the Arahabaki that you're after are \Nclearly rooted in the same incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I think we could achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:34.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,a mutually beneficial relationship \Nsimply by sharing information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,And if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.68,Stray Dogs - Italics,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chuuya, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.87,Stray Dogs - Italics,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.23,Stray Dogs - Italics,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,The Port Mafia caught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.29,Stray Dogs - Italics,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,You can do something, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.44,Stray Dogs - Italics,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and help me, like you always doー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:55.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,An organization bent on retaliation that \Ncontrols prime property in Yokohama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,But even though you're armed with guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,all the members, aside from you,\N are just children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:05.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,As a fellow leader, I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it, Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:15.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The wielder of the greatest violence \Nin this room is Chuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:20.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,But, to the Mafia, violence is \Njust one tool at our disposal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:26.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The Mafia's true nature is to control \Nrational action by a plethora of means.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you lecturing me with that lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind exchanging information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,But you speak first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll decide after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:47.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,We're investigating the rumor that \Nthe previous boss has re-emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:51.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,According to Dazai-kun's information, \Nhe's appeared three times in the past two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:55.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,In each case, he was sighted \Nin Suribachi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth time, yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,he blew you away with black flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,The dead don't come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:08.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, but we no longer have \Nthe luxury of insisting so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,This security footage is of the Port Mafia's vault,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:20.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,the most difficult room to enter in our headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The previous boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:29.04,Stray Dogs - Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I've come back to life from \Nthe burning pits of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.84,Stray Dogs - Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.26,Stray Dogs - Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,He feeds on anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:43.56,Stray Dogs - Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,He summoned me back from Hell with the \Nintention of having me breed even more anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:48.55,Stray Dogs - Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,The beast of the gods, \NArahabaki of the black flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:55.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the footage we have \Nin our security records.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:00.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, very few people \Nknow about this footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strict gag order in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,And suppose the previous \Nboss gave the same speech
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,elsewhere that he did in the video?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:12.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,He says that his death was not \Nby disease but by assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,If the previous boss's supporters\N were to find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,a third of our organization \Nwould become my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:24.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Win or lose, the Port Mafia would be doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:31.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun, what is Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I did a little research of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Arahabaki is a legendary \Nservant of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:42.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,But because they are so old, \Ntheir true form is unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:46.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe in gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:50.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a coincidence that you \Nwere doing research on Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:55.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the same rumors that we did, \Nand you were after the truth. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,We get a lot of drifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no easy way to find \Nthe source of the rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how Suribachi City was made?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The city was built
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:11.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,in the aftermath of an unexplained \Nexplosion at the end of the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:14.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,The explosion was caused \Nby Arahabaki, supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that eight years ago \Na captured foreign soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:24.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,was tortured at a military \Nfacility in the settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:28.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,His rage and hatred summoned Arahabaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:35.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,and the black flame blew up this \Nnation's soldiers, facility and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,That explosion resulted in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Suribachi City as we know it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-kun, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:48.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,They must have used a special \Nability that we don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:53.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If that footage wasn't forged, we're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:58.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-kun, I have an order for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Find the person responsible before they \Ndo the same thing they did on the video
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,in front of the supporters \Nof the previous boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:06.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Am I doing this by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Have Chuuya-kun there give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to work with this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the shit out of you, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kid, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,And you're smaller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to drink some more milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business, bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:46.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I trust that you understand you aren't \Nin a position to refuse my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,If the previous boss's supporters \Nfind out, as my accomplice,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,you will be tortured, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to die easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:00.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that's \Nthe best course of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:03.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,I have several reasons for \Nmaking you work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,First, someone outside of the Port Mafia \Nwill have an easier time interviewing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:12.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun needs to be monitored \Nso he doesn't betray us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:13.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, tell me where we're going, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, would you mind not talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy breathing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rip your head off, you suicidal maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:41.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're interviewing people who \Nwere closest to the explostion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,What explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:48.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A week ago, there was an explosion \Nsimilar to the one we experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It happened nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The previous boss wasn't sighted there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:57.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but the cause is likely the same \Nas what we're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:01.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to talk to a \Nsurvivor of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,A survivor? You mean there were casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A handful of the Port Mafia \Nmembers you so despise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The survivor is gifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You've already met this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit must have \Ngotten to them already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yapping and move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we're going \Nto get an interview here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:45.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your arms and face this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:51.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Our dinner just came to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel like doing \Nan interview anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:22:00.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,It's simpler to beat the guy behind \Nthe cover-up and make him talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Nakahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat the shit out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.97,sign_31816_385_Episode_27,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 27
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.97,sign_31816_386_The_God_of_Fire,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What a child.
